<p class="p1" style="font-size: 2em;">Cookie Policy</p>

<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Does Promo Posts use cookies?</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">Yes, we use cookies and other technologies to optimize the Promo Posts experience. Cookies also help us keep your account safe. By continuing to visit or use our services, you are agreeing to the use of cookies and similar technologies for the purposes we describe in this policy.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">What is a cookie?</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">A cookie is a small file placed onto your device that enables Promo Posts features and functionality. For example, cookies enable us to identify your device, secure your access to Promo Posts and our sites generally, and even help us know if someone attempts to access your account from a different device.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">When does Promo Posts place cookies?</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">We use cookies on our site (<a href="http://PromoPosts.net"><span class="s2">PromoPosts.net</span></a>). Any browser visiting these sites will receive cookies from us.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">What types of cookies does Promo Posts use?</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">We use two types: persistent cookies and session cookies. A persistent cookie helps us recognize you as an existing user, so it&rsquo;s easier to return to Promo Posts or interact with our services without signing in again. After you sign in, a persistent cookie stays in your browser and will be read by Promo Posts when you return to our site. Session cookies only last for as long as the session (usually the current visit to a website or a browser session).</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">What are cookies used for?</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">Cookies can be used to recognize you when you visit Promo Posts, remember your preferences, and give you a personalized experience that&rsquo;s in line with your settings. Cookies also make your interactions with Promo Posts faster and more secure.</span></p>
